      "rdf:value": "<L>1927<pc>9,2<k1>aj<k2>aj<e>1\r\n<s>aj</s> ¦ <ab>cl.</ab> 1. <ab>P.</ab> (<ab>defect.</ab>, supplemented <ab>fr.</ab> √ <s>vI</s>), <s>a/jati</s>, <s>AjIt</s>, <s>ajitum</s>, to drive, propel, throw, cast:\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Desid.</ab> <s>ajijizati</s>, to be desirous of driving <info whitneyroots=\"aj,2\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1P\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
